title: Alabama beat reporters: Grading the Tide secondary five games in
text:
Alabama beat reporters John Talty and Michael Casagrande grade the youthful Alabama secondary after five games in the Wednesday beat reporter show seen above.
See how a quickly improving secondary grades out, check out AL.com's feature on Minkah Fitzpatrick and a gallery of Marlon Humphrey below.
